			<div class="comment-content comment">
				<p><a href="http://gsorman.typepad.com/guy_sorman/2011/01/le-messianisme-fran%C3%A7ais.html">http://gsorman.typepad.com/guy_sorman/2011/01/le-messianisme-fran%C3%A7ais.html</a></p>
			</div>
			<div class="comment-action">
